lead_paragraph: An article on Thursday about Kris Jenkins, a nose tackle for the Jets who developed a passion for cooking while growing up in a single-parent household headed by his father, misspelled the father’s given name. He is Darome Jenkins, not Darmone. The error also appeared in an article on March 16 about Kris Jenkins’s involvement in a nonprofit program that teaches children about life through art.
